title: 求大佬们帮忙看下这个是什么，怎么处理
author: yzh200216
txt_content: 23.01 16:24:55 [服务器] 警告 The updater could not contact dev.bukkit.org for updating.23.01 16:24:55 [服务器] 警告 If you have not recently modified your configuration and this is the first time you are seeing this message, the site may be experiencing temporary downtime.

replies.author: 木守
replies.txt_content: 你的服务端bukkit不能更新，这个问题不影响你正常启动，你可以去问问你的服务商，这个和你插件什么的都没问题
